casebody.data:
Rothschild et al., Appellants, v. Hall et al., Respondents. (Supreme Court, General Term, Third Department. February 18, 1891.)

Argued before Learned, P. J., and Landon and Matham, JJ.

No opinion. Order reversed, with $10 costs and printing disbursements, and motion to vacate injunction denied, with $10 costs.
